sg":"呢個病有個學名...有無人記得係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCFSt44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCFSt44.png&h=dfa74d28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wr1m6RK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWr1m6RK.png&h=e93ff034&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28f92ef5b2f2eb7b95c6087ef0a8cad7d3b26150","tid":2432850,"uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c93b0c6d5ac4f29e62b90f4d995656de5b63d61","tid":2432850,"uid":326032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"以前細個會食牆灰，依家諗起應該係嗰陣時有異食癖<br />\n建議樓主補充返多啲礦物質同微量維生素，食非食物對身體始終唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"零星研究表明，很多異食癖個例是因人體缺乏某種礦物質而引起的，諸如鐵、鋅等。缺鐵症本身有時又是乳糜瀉或鉤蟲感染的結果。此類患者食用的物質常含有其身體所缺乏的礦物質。最近有學者考慮將強迫症歸為異食癖的病因之一。不過目前在被廣泛使用的精神疾病診斷與統計手冊（DSM-IV）中，異食癖仍被認為是一種精神疾病。感知、生理、文化和社會心理等因素也有被用來解釋異食癖的起因。<br />\n<br />\n保重身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df90f88568b14877bef0a3d58ca2de6c743033c","tid":2432850,"uid":4152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"食家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab8d4cf07afc4242e2992b52287d714579b0721","tid":2432850,"uid":388497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"樓主身體有無發生異變<br />\n成個元素週期表你攻略曬未"},{"pid":"2f7c9f4ae38a83dacb20fad6bb93b3aa51a6e908","tid":2432850,"uid":271857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"花槽啲花嘅花蜜"},{"pid":"78bf2f5e446bff5d55a878888d04da3a2d0dc1f2","tid":2432850,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"咬小巴坐椅個紫紅色膠套，諗番起都想嘔，但細個成日都想咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac