其他人有補充/好食既野?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"你形容完都唔知有咩好食, 由其係痕痕地/唔難食都算好食? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比較似分享食後感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"其實大部分野都係一放落口就難食到拎返出黎<br />\n可以做到唔難食已經會食第二次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但標題唔係ok好食咩"},{"pid":"f1c92b7365b71ea2250c72a82bf0a9b5b2586b72","tid":2432850,"uid":229224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"頂盡係食鼻涕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b190895d646c34b13c9c3d24094b281ab4dcf19e","tid":2432850,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f7c9f4ae38a83dacb20fad6bb93b3aa51a6e908","tid":2432850,"uid":271857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"花槽啲花嘅花蜜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"紅色果隻？"},{"pid":"46d3f76936bedb4d4d7764d72a951677a86e65f5","tid":2432850,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"啊仲有一樣唔錯既野就係橙味牙膏<br />\n果種香味你會忍唔住吞左幾啖<br />\n<br />\n但其他味唔好食"},{"pid":"fdcd8a32e955e645ebd6963a57724cc228d8ed7d","tid":2432850,"uid":72195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"好細個試過咬銀仔，陣銀味同聞落去差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擦膠好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼻屎細個必食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家諗起都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b